.name
Burf
.author
Michael Tanzer 
.version
1.00
.description
A BackUp ReFresher written in Rexx.  Designed to maintain backups of
important directories between full volume backups.  Copies only new and
modified files, using either archive flags or date comparison.  Can
optionally delete from the backup any files and subdirectories not found in
the original.  
